{"tid":2002083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記錄港反送中運動，路透社奪普立茲獎","createTime":"2020-05-05T03:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T04:36:51.000Z","uid":69696,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6acfe640691055f0adcd39f9b7fb6b7812c3041e","tid":2002083,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T03:56:22.000Z","msg":"美國「新聞界奧斯卡」普立茲獎周一揭曉本年度得獎名單，路透社憑報道去年香港反送中運動，榮獲「突發新聞圖片獎」。<br />\n普立茲獎評審委員會讚揚路透社，其港人抗議中國政府侵犯公民自由以及捍衞自治的新聞圖片「廣泛而有啟發性」。<br />\n<br />\n幫手禁入蘋果link睇新聞：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200505/E27QBAFHOJK5QDR4A6L3PJG2CA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200505%2FE27QBAFHOJK5QDR4A6L3PJG2CA%2F&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktZS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=8de2079c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200505%2FE27QBAFHOJK5QDR4A6L3PJG2CA%2F&h=9f993b95\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200505/E27QBAFHOJK5QDR4A6L3PJG2CA/</a><br />\n得獎圖片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/news/picture/reuters-wins-pulitzer-prize-for-breaking-idUSRTX7H87E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fnews%2Fpicture%2Freuters-wins-pulitzer-prize-for-breaking-idUSRTX7H87E&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktZS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=09268f93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fnews%2Fpicture%2Freuters-wins-pulitzer-prize-for-breaking-idUSRTX7H87E&h=b39b22e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/news/picture/reuters-wins-pulitzer-prize-for-breaking-idUSRTX7H87E</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pulitzer.org/winners/photography-staff-reuters-2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pulitzer.org%2Fwinners%2Fphotography-staff-reuters-2&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktZS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=ab1184d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pulitzer.org/winners/photography-staff-reuters-2</a><br />